mory is now current. Future heartbeats can reference these findings without re-running analysis. 5.5h until 19h session.\n\n## 2026-03-30 13:08 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 1] V4.1 Day 1 Results: +$7.92 (3W/2L) + Indicator Logging Fix\n\n**Task:** Compile V4.1 Day 1 morning session results. Fix enhanced outcome logging.\n\n**V4.1 Morning Session (11:00-13:00 UTC):**\n- **Trades: 6 total** (5 logged in outcomes, 1 missing due to restart)\n- **Results: 4W/2L = 67% WR**\n- **Balance: $922.45 \u2192 $930.37 = +$7.92**\n- **12:43 clean trade (post-fix):** YES $12.10 @ 0.474 \u2192 \u2705 WIN (+$13.44 payout)\n  - OBI\u2705(+0.69), CVD\u2705, MACD\u2705, VWAP\u274c \u2014 VWAP disagreed but 12h = relaxed hour\n  - Copy bullish@100 \u2014 attention signal theory holds (high conf = WIN)\n\n**Bug fix #2: Indicator logging race condition**\n- `_last_indicators` was being read at OUTCOME time (5 min later), not TRADE time\n- By outcome check, `_last_indicators` was overwritten by subsequent `should_trade()` calls\n- Fix: capture indicators dict at trade execution, pass to `_check_outcome()` as frozen copy\n- Bot restarted at 13:10 with fix. Next trade will have full indica",
